channel.title: Auto Typer - Made by Sparkytycoon™
channel.description:
Before you even read. Take a moment and read this first. I created this. I did not steal this. It belongs %100 to me, Sparkytycoon™. I am a registered business. You are not aloud to steal this program or any of its contents.
This is a cool Auto-Typer program. It repeats sentences or any typer of text. Like on private servers, using commands over and over. This doesn't have a multiline function though. That will be release this upcoming week. It will not be free though, as i would like to make even a little bit of profit from my work. I dont recomend using this for spamming, but you will anyways. You can set your own times or choose a pre selected one. This has an "Auto-Enter" feature, so it wont just appear in your box and not send it. If you want to use the manual time select. its in Milliseconds. "1000" is 1 second. You can go lower down to "0001"
There is also an extra download for my NotePad.... Its just a basic one. I am creating the NotePad Pro now. It wont be free of course. Though all my products are cheap. As paying $5 dollars for a NotePad is OutRagious. Both the products are sold seperately at $1 each. There is a registry too. So you cant buy it and give it to your friends. :D I wish i had pictures but eh, i got too lazy. Please if you do not trust me. Download it, Scan it, If there is a virus call the cops on me. As i have no virus injected on there. Neither of them. If their is a virus, take a pic of the scan and post it. Once posted i will remove this topic. But i will validate the virus pic. Dont try to scam them all out of downloading it because you cant make one or you just dont know how to handle communications.
Please dont post hate comments. You come in. Dont even read it calling it stupid because its an auto typer. Just dont even read it. You are wasting your time. Because all your doing is calling something dumb over the internet. It doesnt hurt anybody.
